{"tid":603751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打做人做到好行屍走肉","createTime":"2018-03-24T04:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T04:10:56.000Z","uid":120847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68af43f3c5c63f830da66b3f118f4c3e011982f0","tid":603751,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"25歲, 係正苦做個officer, 日日返工重重覆覆<br />\n錢銀上都算夠食夠飲, 但買樓就不了, 想做多少少野搞下生意仔/投資下更加唔洗諗<br />\n個人又獨來獨往, 鐘意咩都一條友自己做, 應該呢世人都唔會結婚生仔<br />\n有時都唔知生活為乜<br />\n<br />\n呢排搵緊有咩小國適合退休, 歐洲呀南美呀東南亞果啲,<br />\n諗緊好唔好草夠錢就去呢啲小國, 係沙灘到開間餐廳仔過人世"},{"pid":"eb33cebe31003fd6f3971c843a8acab426149386","tid":603751,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"25歲正苦officer幾多人恨都恨唔到"},{"pid":"5be9e19ff767730ed29d19466a2edb0d64ac0de2","tid":603751,"uid":132210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"就係想過你既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b50e9261a889af302705054660ae895d74f5fd7","tid":603751,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"依加好似對好多野都提唔起興趣<br />\n岩岩出黎做野時, 每個星期都好期待Happy Friday同一班朋友去飲酒直落<br />\n依加已經冇晒興致, 個人悶到有時一條友去酒吧睇下波聽下music都唔想出去見人<br />\n以前一有時間同錢就會一條友去旅行<br />\n依加好似覺得地方度度都差唔多, 冇晒興致, 放假係屋企鳩fing算"},{"pid":"b91da672c54fdd180c7776a77a49dcd7731405df","tid":603751,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"Officer 人生勝利組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a68cadde359bb6bb699fa3bede6857039a0f76","tid":603751,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:10: